    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable transportation option. The exterior shows some visible scratches and minor dings consistent with its age and mileage, and the interior has some noticeable wear but remains functional. Mechanically, it runs well and has been maintained for regular use, though it may eventually need some minor cosmetic or mechanical attention. It\u2019s a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable car at an affordable price point.",
      "price": 21500.0,
